            <h2>Ordering Instructions</h2>
            <p>Please read the following instructions prior to ordering.</p>
            <h3>To order</h3>
            <p>First select your CATEGORY from the list on the left to display all the products for that section. From the list, you are able to view the items in detail by clicking on the thumbnail image or by clicking on ORDER NOW. To begin ordering the items, first select the size, quantity etc then click on ADD TO CART, repeating this process with other items will continue to add your selections to your order.</p>
            <p>To complete your order follow the CHECK OUT instructions below, if you wish to edit or view your order prior to Check Out then see the Editing and viewing Orders section below.</p>
            <h3>Editing and Viewing Orders</h3>
            <p>You can edit and view your selections from the VIEW CART page accessed from the VIEW CART link on the left. To update a quantity, enter new quantity and click the 'UPDATE CART' button</p>
            <p>To delete a product from the VIEW CART list, click on REMOVE ITEM on the right of each item and click on the 'UPDATE CART' button</p>
            <p>To delete the entire order simply log out without clicking PROCESS ORDER.</p>
            <h4>Check Out</h4>
            <p>To proceed with an order click on the VIEW CART listed on the left. This will display your items. You can now proceed by clicking PROCESS ORDER.</p>
